headline: QR Code Printers Market Outlook Report 2025-2034 | Innovations Focus on Compact, Network-Ready QR Code Printers with ERP Integration
summary: The QR Code Printers Market, valued at USD 446.4 million in 2024, is projected to reach USD 817.1 million by 2032, growing at a CAGR of 7.85%. Driving factors include e-commerce, contactless payments, and regulatory needs. Challenges include price competition and integration complexity. Key trends highlight innovations in compact, network-enabled printers. Major players like Zebra Technologies introduce advanced products, meeting demands across retail, logistics, and healthcare.
